637
00:32:08,319 --> 00:32:09,240
During my two trips to Guizhou,

638
00:32:09,480 --> 00:32:10,839
I saw the county hospital doctors

639
00:32:12,240 --> 00:32:12,839
improve tremendously.

640
00:32:13,160 --> 00:32:13,720
Their foundations may be weaker,

641
00:32:13,839 --> 00:32:14,480
