649
00:32:33,759 --> 00:32:34,279
Dr. Ye and the others.

650
00:32:34,640 --> 00:32:35,720
And MyAmpere.

651
00:32:36,160 --> 00:32:37,480
They've agreed

652
00:32:37,720 --> 00:32:38,599
