657
00:32:55,799 --> 00:32:56,319
Sure.

658
00:32:56,640 --> 00:32:57,119
What are you going for?

659
00:32:58,440 --> 00:32:58,799
To join your free clinic.

660
00:32:59,599 --> 00:33:00,119
And to see

661
00:33:01,240 --> 00:33:01,640
