667
00:33:13,640 --> 00:33:14,640
Drinking water.

668
00:33:14,880 --> 00:33:15,240
Have some water.

669
00:33:16,359 --> 00:33:16,680
Who wants water?

670
00:33:17,119 --> 00:33:18,079
Put it down.

671
00:33:18,079 --> 00:33:18,799
