672
00:33:20,799 --> 00:33:21,200
Yes.

673
00:33:21,640 --> 00:33:22,319
I don't have plans this weekend anyway.

674
00:33:22,839 --> 00:33:23,319
That's great.

675
00:33:23,920 --> 00:33:24,839
Dr. Ye,

676
00:33:29,519 --> 00:33:30,039
