677
00:33:30,680 --> 00:33:31,599
Okay.

678
00:33:31,640 --> 00:33:32,319
Director,

679
00:33:32,839 --> 00:33:33,759
can I join you

680
00:33:33,799 --> 00:33:34,319
at the free clinic too?

681
00:33:34,799 --> 00:33:35,440
Sure.

682
00:33:35,480 --> 00:33:36,680
Of course you can.

683
00:33:36,720 --> 00:33:37,359
Go ahead.

684
00:33:37,759 --> 00:33:38,279
And don't come back.

685
00:33:38,359 --> 00:33:39,359
How about this?

686
00:33:39,400 --> 00:33:40,000
Du and Ye

687
00:33:40,160 --> 00:33:41,279
have both been here a while.

688
00:33:41,920 --> 00:33:42,640
Let's rotate them

689
00:33:42,960 --> 00:33:43,519
