692
00:33:47,440 --> 00:33:47,920
to learn.

693
00:33:53,200 --> 00:33:53,920
I believe

694
00:33:54,160 --> 00:33:55,319
future cardiologists

695
00:33:56,759 --> 00:33:57,319
should, in any case,

696
00:33:57,640 --> 00:33:58,319
be trained in both medicine and surgery.

697
00:33:58,400 --> 00:33:59,079
I'm fine with that.

698
00:33:59,319 --> 00:33:59,680
Can you handle it?

699
00:34:00,039 --> 00:34:01,240
I can.

700
00:34:01,480 --> 00:34:02,519
The last person who said that

701
00:34:02,519 --> 00:34:03,279
was...

702
00:34:05,559 --> 00:34:05,960
Hurry up.

703
00:34:06,519 --> 00:34:07,599
Thank you, Dr. Zhou.

704
00:34:07,599 --> 00:34:08,039
Thank you, Dr. Zhou.

705
00:34:08,840 --> 00:34:09,760
Du, you'll be fine

706
00:34:10,159 --> 00:34:10,880
coming to my department.

707
00:34:11,360 --> 00:34:11,920
Okay.

708
00:34:12,079 --> 00:34:12,920
But at your current stage,

709
00:34:14,440 --> 00:34:15,400
I want to arrange

710
00:34:15,639 --> 00:34:16,719
