716
00:34:25,840 --> 00:34:26,760
Sure.

717
00:34:26,760 --> 00:34:27,119
No problem on my end.

718
00:34:27,599 --> 00:34:28,079
Thank you, both of you.

719
00:34:28,840 --> 00:34:29,679
Thank you, both doctors.

720
00:34:30,159 --> 00:34:31,079
Director,

721
00:34:32,079 --> 00:34:32,920
why don't I get

722
00:34:33,360 --> 00:34:33,960
