729
00:34:45,159 --> 00:34:46,679
Liu Dong. Who else?

730
00:34:53,840 --> 00:34:54,159
Since it's been approved,

731
00:34:55,480 --> 00:34:56,119
you two can

732
00:34:56,400 --> 00:34:56,800
take the second shift

733
00:34:58,719 --> 00:35:00,039
