734
00:35:00,880 --> 00:35:01,519
That'd be great.

735
00:35:01,960 --> 00:35:02,440
I'll tell him right away.

736
00:35:04,119 --> 00:35:04,400
Director Lin has no objections, right?

737
00:35:04,400 --> 00:35:05,199
I...

738
00:35:05,639 --> 00:35:06,480
Should I have any objections?

739
00:35:08,119 --> 00:35:09,760
It's a perfectly reasonable arrangement.

740
00:35:10,280 --> 00:35:10,599
Come in.

741
00:35:11,079 --> 00:35:11,920
Director, you wanted to see me?

742
00:35:12,400 --> 00:35:13,000
Come in.

743
00:35:14,000 --> 00:35:15,320
I brought you a coffee.

744
00:35:15,760 --> 00:35:17,480
A hot latte.

745
00:35:18,000 --> 00:35:18,800
Thank you.

746
00:35:19,480 --> 00:35:20,440
There's a

747
00:35:22,000 --> 00:35:22,960
TAVR training course.

748
00:35:24,880 --> 00:35:25,400
I've registered you.

749
00:35:26,239 --> 00:35:27,599
TAVR?

750
00:35:27,840 --> 00:35:28,599
Yes.

751
00:35:28,719 --> 00:35:30,039
The leadership speeches

752
00:35:30,519 --> 00:35:31,599
