753
00:35:32,039 --> 00:35:32,880
You can go in the afternoon.

754
00:35:33,000 --> 00:35:33,880
They've arranged

755
00:35:34,360 --> 00:35:35,800
a live surgical demonstration.

756
00:35:38,159 --> 00:35:38,679
It won't affect your Saturday clinic.

757
00:35:38,760 --> 00:35:39,719
All right.

758
00:35:39,920 --> 00:35:40,320
I'll go Friday afternoon.

759
00:35:40,920 --> 00:35:41,519
Good.

760
00:35:54,679 --> 00:35:54,960
Hello?

761
00:35:55,079 --> 00:35:55,719
Director Sheng.

762
00:35:57,760 --> 00:35:59,239
Lin Yi will come Friday afternoon.

763
00:35:59,679 --> 00:36:00,599
I'm leaving him in your hands.

764
00:36:01,840 --> 00:36:02,119
All right.

765
00:36:02,280 --> 00:36:02,840
I know what to do.

766
00:36:03,480 --> 00:36:04,159
Then I'll schedule

767
00:36:04,199 --> 00:36:05,400
the most complicated case

768
00:36:05,440 --> 00:36:06,599
for Friday afternoon.

769
00:36:07,079 --> 00:36:07,519
Good.

770
00:36:08,280 --> 00:36:08,639
Wait.

771
00:36:10,199 --> 00:36:11,360
If possible,

772
00:36:11,960 --> 00:36:13,440
could you schedule

773
00:36:13,719 --> 00:36:14,719
the case you mentioned

774
00:36:16,280 --> 00:36:17,360
for Saturday morning instead?

775
00:36:17,960 --> 00:36:18,400
No problem, Director Sheng.

776
00:36:26,840 --> 00:36:27,719
Thank you.

777
00:36:27,760 --> 00:36:28,559
Cardiac surgeons

778
00:36:28,599 --> 00:36:29,719
have a clear advantage

779
00:36:29,960 --> 00:36:30,840
when performing TAVR.

780
00:36:30,880 --> 00:36:32,039
We already have

781
00:36:32,199 --> 00:36:32,920
a strong understanding

782
00:36:33,159 --> 00:36:33,639
of cardiac anatomy.

783
00:36:33,800 --> 00:36:35,239
So

784
00:36:35,320 --> 00:36:36,519
we can better understand

785
00:36:36,760 --> 00:36:38,320
and master this technique.

786
00:36:38,440 --> 00:36:39,199
If an accident occurs

787
00:36:39,480 --> 00:36:40,360
during the intervention,

788
00:36:40,360 --> 00:36:41,639
we can

789
00:36:42,119 --> 00:36:43,000
immediately perform a rescue procedure.

790
00:36:43,239 --> 00:36:44,800
All right. Now

791
00:36:44,800 --> 00:36:45,800
we're entering

792
00:36:46,480 --> 00:36:47,519
the most critical part of the intervention:

793
00:36:48,440 --> 00:36:50,159
advancing the valve stent across the arch.

794
00:36:50,800 --> 00:36:52,320
This patient's aortic arch is very steep,

795
00:36:53,519 --> 00:36:54,400
so crossing it may be difficult.

796
00:36:54,679 --> 00:36:55,559
Look at that arch.

797
00:36:57,760 --> 00:36:58,400
It really is too steep.

798
00:37:02,039 --> 00:37:02,559
Add a little curve.

799
00:37:03,559 --> 00:37:03,920
A little more.

800
00:37:18,559 --> 00:37:19,119
Good.

801
00:37:20,559 --> 00:37:21,320
We're in position.

802
00:37:21,679 --> 00:37:22,480
Beautiful.

803
00:37:22,559 --> 00:37:22,920
Director An truly deserves

804
00:37:22,920 --> 00:37:23,400
his reputation as a TAVR expert.

805
00:37:23,679 --> 00:37:24,559
That was incredible.

806
00:37:24,559 --> 00:37:25,239
Excellent work.

807
00:37:25,320 --> 00:37:26,400
Textbook standard.

808
00:37:29,920 --> 00:37:30,400
Hello.

809
00:37:30,960 --> 00:37:32,000
Director An, that was amazing.

810
00:37:32,079 --> 00:37:32,559
You're too kind.

811
00:37:33,559 --> 00:37:34,480
Beautiful procedure.

812
00:37:34,719 --> 00:37:35,119
You're too kind.

813
00:37:36,400 --> 00:37:36,960
Lin Yi.

814
00:37:37,239 --> 00:37:37,960
Director Lin.

815
00:37:38,840 --> 00:37:39,199
Hello.

816
00:37:41,199 --> 00:37:42,199
Director An, you know me?

817
00:37:42,360 --> 00:37:43,400
Every cardiac surgeon knows

818
00:37:43,559 --> 00:37:44,239
the famous Director Lin

819
00:37:44,320 --> 00:37:45,480
from Dongli Hospital.

820
00:37:46,039 --> 00:37:46,800
You just rarely

821
00:37:46,800 --> 00:37:47,639
attend conferences.

822
00:37:49,320 --> 00:37:50,719
Your elite team with Director Zhou

823
00:37:50,840 --> 00:37:51,840
is renowned

824
00:37:51,960 --> 00:37:53,199
throughout the field.

825
00:37:54,159 --> 00:37:55,639
Really? We're that famous?

826
00:37:56,039 --> 00:37:57,199
Absolutely.

827
00:37:58,440 --> 00:37:59,280
For next week's procedure,

828
00:37:59,280 --> 00:38:00,400
you'll be using a new drug-coated balloon.

829
00:38:00,639 --> 00:38:01,519
Coordinate with Ouyang Da

830
00:38:01,519 --> 00:38:02,159
in advance

831
00:38:02,400 --> 00:38:03,000
and make sure everything is ready.

832
00:38:03,960 --> 00:38:05,199
You're using MyAmpere again?

833
00:38:05,199 --> 00:38:05,880
What's wrong?

834
00:38:08,360 --> 00:38:08,840
Lately,

835
00:38:10,119 --> 00:38:10,719
our department has used

836
00:38:10,760 --> 00:38:12,000
a lot of MyAmpere products.

837
00:38:12,000 --> 00:38:12,559
Aixin康

838
00:38:13,199 --> 00:38:14,119
is starting to complain.

839
00:38:14,119 --> 00:38:14,800
When we suddenly need

840
00:38:15,320 --> 00:38:16,159
supplies or support,

841
00:38:16,199 --> 00:38:17,239
they're becoming

842
00:38:18,199 --> 00:38:19,719
less responsive.

843
00:38:20,320 --> 00:38:22,119
Their sales rep

844
00:38:22,400 --> 00:38:23,320
has also been making

845
00:38:23,360 --> 00:38:24,280
veiled complaints.

846
00:38:24,519 --> 00:38:26,119
Maybe this time

847
00:38:26,440 --> 00:38:27,800
