854
00:38:44,199 --> 00:38:44,559
Director,

855
00:38:45,639 --> 00:38:46,679
but recently

856
00:38:47,079 --> 00:38:49,239
I've heard some gossip.

857
00:38:49,800 --> 00:38:50,559
What gossip?

858
00:38:50,880 --> 00:38:51,480
Just

859
00:38:52,079 --> 00:38:53,639
