863
00:38:59,440 --> 00:39:00,079
And

864
00:39:00,519 --> 00:39:01,079
inside the department,

865
00:39:02,119 --> 00:39:03,199
I've heard

866
00:39:03,239 --> 00:39:04,039
similar remarks too.

867
00:39:09,760 --> 00:39:10,639
Then ask Aixin康

868
00:39:10,639 --> 00:39:11,440
for their materials as well.

869
00:39:12,079 --> 00:39:12,840
Compare both products

870
00:39:13,079 --> 00:39:13,960
carefully.

871
00:39:14,760 --> 00:39:15,320
Understood, Director.

872
00:39:19,039 --> 00:39:19,639
We have another live surgery

873
00:39:19,639 --> 00:39:21,000
