874
00:39:21,280 --> 00:39:21,960
Can you come?

875
00:39:23,039 --> 00:39:25,199
Tomorrow morning may not work.

876
00:39:25,320 --> 00:39:25,760
I have something else.

877
00:39:26,880 --> 00:39:27,840
That's a shame,

878
00:39:28,320 --> 00:39:29,519
