892
00:39:50,440 --> 00:39:51,320
Very rarely.

893
00:39:55,599 --> 00:39:56,119
Well...

894
00:39:56,159 --> 00:39:57,119
I need to take this call.

895
00:39:57,159 --> 00:39:57,639
Excuse me.

896
00:40:00,280 --> 00:40:00,639
Hello?

897
00:40:00,880 --> 00:40:01,400
What's up?

898
00:40:02,599 --> 00:40:03,840
How do you want to get there tomorrow?

899
00:40:04,639 --> 00:40:05,960
Take the bus with everyone,

900
00:40:06,159 --> 00:40:06,760
or should I drive

901
00:40:06,800 --> 00:40:07,480
and the two of us go together?

902
00:40:10,519 --> 00:40:11,159
Well...

903
00:40:11,480 --> 00:40:13,000
I may not

904
00:40:13,400 --> 00:40:15,519
be able to go tomorrow.

905
00:40:17,079 --> 00:40:17,599
Why?

906
00:40:18,760 --> 00:40:22,159
I... I'm not feeling well.

907
00:40:23,199 --> 00:40:23,920
What's wrong?

908
00:40:24,440 --> 00:40:25,239
How are you...

909
00:40:25,559 --> 00:40:26,079
I...

910
00:40:27,639 --> 00:40:28,679
My stomach.

911
00:40:29,679 --> 00:40:31,239
My stomach hurts.

912
00:40:32,039 --> 00:40:32,599
Stomach pain?

913
00:40:33,639 --> 00:40:34,519
When did it start?

914
00:40:36,920 --> 00:40:39,199
Yesterday, I think. I'm fine.

915
00:40:40,159 --> 00:40:40,960
What do you mean, fine?

916
00:40:41,639 --> 00:40:42,679
You know heart problems

917
00:40:42,679 --> 00:40:43,119
can sometimes

918
00:40:43,119 --> 00:40:44,079
present as stomach pain.

919
00:40:44,199 --> 00:40:45,360
Where are you? I'll come find you.

920
00:40:45,519 --> 00:40:46,800
No, no. Don't come.

921
00:40:46,840 --> 00:40:48,920
I'm outside.

922
00:40:49,239 --> 00:40:50,440
I'm fine. I'm a doctor too.

923
00:40:50,440 --> 00:40:51,519
I know very well

924
00:40:51,519 --> 00:40:52,159
whether stomach pain is heart-related.

925
00:40:52,719 --> 00:40:54,599
I'll just drink some hot water.

926
00:40:57,639 --> 00:40:58,199
I'm really fine.

927
00:40:58,840 --> 00:40:59,199
Nothing's wrong.

928
00:41:00,599 --> 00:41:01,119
Director Lin.

929
00:41:02,559 --> 00:41:03,079
Director An.

930
00:41:03,519 --> 00:41:04,760
Professor Luo's surgery tomorrow morning

931
00:41:04,760 --> 00:41:05,920
is still being held here. Don't forget.

932
00:41:06,519 --> 00:41:07,599
Ten o'clock. See you tomorrow.

933
00:41:13,159 --> 00:41:13,559
All right.

934
00:41:14,639 --> 00:41:15,239
Good to hear you're fine.

935
00:41:15,760 --> 00:41:16,440
Take care of yourself.

936
00:41:16,920 --> 00:41:17,519
Get some rest.

937
00:41:19,760 --> 00:41:21,239
Okay. Okay.

938
00:41:23,840 --> 00:41:25,519
He suddenly called me,

939
00:41:25,760 --> 00:41:26,920
all anxious and rushed.

940
00:41:27,480 --> 00:41:28,679
My mind went blank,

941
00:41:29,599 --> 00:41:30,559
and I blurted everything out.

942
00:41:31,119 --> 00:41:31,599
Look at you.

943
00:41:31,719 --> 00:41:32,519
You're attending a training course.

944
00:41:32,760 --> 00:41:34,039
Why couldn't you just tell him?

945
00:41:35,440 --> 00:41:36,199
At our hospital,

946
00:41:36,679 --> 00:41:37,639
isn't Cardiology the one

947
00:41:38,239 --> 00:41:39,920
that performs TAVR?

948
00:41:40,280 --> 00:41:41,800
Now Cardiac Surgery wants to do it too,

949
00:41:41,960 --> 00:41:42,960
and I'm the one learning.

950
00:41:46,159 --> 00:41:48,199
It felt like I was betraying him.

951
00:41:48,519 --> 00:41:49,719
You're overthinking it.

952
00:41:49,880 --> 00:41:50,800
Work is work.

953
00:41:50,920 --> 00:41:52,360
Everyone is trying to save patients.

954
00:41:52,679 --> 00:41:54,320
Pretending to be sick and lying to him

955
00:41:54,559 --> 00:41:55,599
is what could actually hurt your relationship.

956
00:41:56,960 --> 00:41:58,199
Who knew we'd run into

957
00:41:58,239 --> 00:41:59,760
Professor Luo returning to operate?

958
00:42:00,119 --> 00:42:01,559
It's a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity.

959
00:42:05,079 --> 00:42:05,760
Do you think

960
00:42:07,000 --> 00:42:09,320
he'll really hold it against me?

961
00:42:09,440 --> 00:42:10,280
Probably not.

962
00:42:11,000 --> 00:42:11,760
How about

963
00:42:14,480 --> 00:42:15,639
you eat a little less?

964
00:42:16,840 --> 00:42:18,320
I'm tasting it for Xiaorui.

965
00:42:18,320 --> 00:42:18,639
Is that okay?

966
00:42:18,639 --> 00:42:19,440
Besides, he can't eat

967
00:42:19,440 --> 00:42:20,280
all of this anyway.

968
00:42:27,199 --> 00:42:28,519
Help me explain it to him

969
00:42:28,800 --> 00:42:29,320
and smooth things over.

970
00:42:29,760 --> 00:42:30,599
He'll be mad at me.

971
00:42:30,639 --> 00:42:31,719
He's never mad at you.

972
00:42:34,760 --> 00:42:35,519
You don't always have to

973
00:42:35,519 --> 00:42:36,360
be our peacemaker.

974
00:42:37,719 --> 00:42:38,599
I just don't want

975
00:42:38,599 --> 00:42:39,719
the two of you to fight.

976
00:42:45,400 --> 00:42:46,039
I know.

977
00:42:47,519 --> 00:42:48,719
You're the best sister.

978
00:42:50,239 --> 00:42:51,679
You don't have to be everyone's confidante.

979
00:42:52,119 --> 00:42:53,199
No one is born

980
00:42:53,199 --> 00:42:54,119
to be a little sun,

981
00:42:54,719 --> 00:42:56,280
always warming and lighting others.

982
00:42:58,119 --> 00:42:59,000
I'm not going.
